title: Can't play ranked.
body:
Hey i just hit level 30 but i can't play ranked. It keeps giving me error message telling me i need at least 16 champions but i have 16 so why can't i play?

http://imgur.com/a/uZd6o 
and
http://imgur.com/a/LE2Bp

replies.body: Good eyes WoWannabe.  Indeed, Singed is currently disabled so your pool will be under 15.  There are some champion sales right now if you want to fill up your pool.  I also noticed you don't have [Facebook Tristana](https://www.facebook.com/leagueoflegends) and [Unchained Alistar](https://www.youtube.com/user/RiotGamesInc) promotional content, which you can unlock for some extras.  I hope that helps!

I really need to change my name... SWO Wannabe just doesn't work with the LoL crowd.

But glad to help! {{sticker:slayer-pantheon-thumbs}}
Ah i see. Thank you for the answer.
Singed is currently disabled and is thus unavailable to count as your 16th champion.
